OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fbecoming largely cloud free, allowing
OL,7,Fa sunny end to the day for most places
OL,8,Fand then a clear night with the wind
OL,9,Feasing. Some patchy mist may develop
OL,10,Fin places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSunny start for most places,
OL,13,Fwith any early mist quickly clearing.
OL,14,FCloud then spreads across the region,
OL,15,Fbut it will remain dry, bright and
OL,16,Fwarm or very warm. Breezy.
